{"type":"text","timestamp":1775874933908,"sessionID":"ses_2859de5fcffeACVHJyPDf0z2hj","part":{"id":"prt_d7a64ec3c0011hj80fzhwS1YQ8","messageID":"msg_d7a64d260001k8jALxroH3L662","sessionID":"ses_2859de5fcffeACVHJyPDf0z2hj","type":"text","text":"I've written the proposal.md file for **AR-016 вҖ” PicoD ж–Үд»¶з®ЎзҗҶ API**. The proposal includes:\n\n**Key Sections:**\n- **Purpose**: File upload/download, directory listing, file operations, path security, and quota management\n- **Scope**: In-scope (upload/download, CRUD operations, quota tracking) and out-of-scope items (HTTP server, authentication, encryption at rest)\n- **Design**: File structure (~1,210 total lines), architecture diagram, and comprehensive type definitions including `FileManager` interface, `UploadRequest/Result`, `DownloadRequest/Result`, `ListRequest/Result`, and `QuotaInfo`\n- **Execution Flows**: Step-by-step diagrams for upload (small & chunked), download, directory listing, and file deletion\n- **Path Security**: Validation rules, workspace isolation, symlink resolution, and traversal prevention\n- **Error Handling**: 12 domain-specific error types with `FileError` structure\n- **Impact Analysis**: 8 new files, dependencies on `pkg/sandbox` and `pkg/store`, and performance characteristics\n- **Alternatives Considered**: 4 alternatives evaluated (direct sandbox access, SFTP, containerd, event-driven)\n- **Risks and Mitigations**: 8 risks with mitigation strategies\n- **Verification**: Test commands and 14 test scenarios\n- **Success Criteria**: 11 criteria including 85% test coverage","time":{"start":1775874933906,"end":1775874933906}}}
